nodes.bodyText:
For efficiency reanson we can think of doing a ReadFileRemoteOperation when we're within the needsDownload condition and are opening write only. So:
if (needsDownload) {
  if (writeOnly) {
    <ReadFileRemoteOperation + storeMetadata>
  } else {
   <DownloadFileOperation  + storeMetadata + storeContents>
  }
}


But that would give us more clutter.

